      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SWING BY (1) is having her first look at this track. In the money last start when second (17.62) at Taree Super Track over 300m. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Can measure up this time. NOAH'S BOY (8) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Hit the board with a minor placing last time when third (17.38) at this track. Expected to be in this for a long way. CATCH MY SHADOW (2) boasts a strong record this journey with six wins and two minors from 15 tries. Was out of placings last time (17.97) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing seventh and beaten 13 lengths. Can hit the frame with the right run. BUTCHER (5) is worth consideration after filling a hole at this course and distance last start.",
